==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Drugget
<hw>Drug"get</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>droguet</ets>, prop. dim. of <ets>drogue</ets> trash, stuff, perh,
the same word as <ets>drogue</ets> drug, but cf. also W. <ets>drwg</ets>
evil, bad, Ir. & Gael. <ets>droch</ets>, Arm. <ets>droug</ets>,
<ets>drouk</ets>. See 3d <er>Drug</er>.]</ety> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>A
coarse woolen cloth dyed of one color or printed on one side; generally
used as a covering for carpets.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>By extension,
any material used for the same purpose.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>druggist</ent>⟦br⟧
